////[ aidewatcher

Runs AIDE filesystem integrity checker and reports violations via speech. Run with cron.


////[ blue-cmd

Checks if a bluetooth device is in range and executes a specified command if it's gone.
It can for example be used to lock or shutdown your computer if you leave place carring your bluetooth enabled mobile phone with you.


////[ loginwatcher

Reports failed logins by speech and shut down system after 3 failed logins. Runs as daemon.


////[ snortwatcher

Report attacks found by snort via speech. Runs as daemon.


////[ Requirements:

- festival
- aide
- snort
